<td><FONT SIZE="1" FACE="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" COLOR="#00AAFF">Originally posted by Thundarbreath on 04-14-2000 04:29 PM<BR></FONT>
<TEXTAREA NAME="EditedMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">Some of the paineel quests are very vague.  Sern Adolia in the Clerics guild will summon the avatar of fright.  He needs the flesh of a zombie (not sure if he means zombie skin...I havent completed this quest yet), embalming dust (I got mine off a gypsie vendor in the oasis but many players also offered to sell me some), charred bone chips from a flaming skeleton...which he says wanders somewhere in Ro...turns out that it is Southern Ro, no Northern Ro...at location neg 450, neg 200 is a ruined temple...if you keep killing the skeletons and mummies that spawn here eventually a named skeleton will spawn, obretl it think is the name...he drops the charred bone chips.  Finally he asks for a vial of Tunares Breath.  The vial is from a druid named Kalayia somewhere in the Faydarks...I havent found Kalayia yet..but I have been camping a spot just outside of Mistmoore....there is an abandoned druid ring...I'm guessing she spawns there....If anyone knows please respond to this message.</TEXTAREA>
